{"tid":1915192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被促下台 林鄭：玩得開心啲","createTime":"2020-03-08T04:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:15:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6db58b5d89e029ea6d93079c8a917a183bf3fd8","tid":1915192,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/XIH5DBV5MRJGWWECDPITCNVPJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2FXIH5DBV5MRJGWWECDPITCNVPJU%2F&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bwyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=40056480\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2FXIH5DBV5MRJGWWECDPITCNVPJU%2F&h=1cb1ab0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/XIH5DBV5MRJGWWECDPITCNVPJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n被促下台 林鄭：玩得開心啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200308/large/1583597834_b2f9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200308%2Flarge%2F1583597834_b2f9.gif&h=a25ceaf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭和隨員踩入郊野公園，全程沒戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】擅長打小報告的特首林鄭月娥昨走出鍵盤work from hill，在環境局局長黃錦星、漁護署署長梁肇輝及一眾隨員陪同下，浩浩蕩蕩踩入大帽山及大欖郊野公園。根據政府新聞處提供的照片，她和隨員全程沒戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無罩通山走<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：至尊公主21人染疫 特朗普倡全體留船<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥其後發新聞稿，呼籲市民在疫情期間郊遊時應保持適當社交距離。根據衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君早前建議，防疫措施包括人與人之間應保持兩米距離。但從昨日相片及影片所見，林鄭與一眾隨員不僅沒戴口罩，彼此間的距離亦不足半米。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港民意研究所最近一次的特首民望調查，林鄭支持度跌至18.21的歷史新低。有讀者向本報說，<span style=\"color: orange;\">昨晨在荃錦管理站遇見林鄭，於是問她何時下台，「佢笑笑口答：玩得開心啲」</span>。林鄭其後在facebook專頁發佈與大帽山茶水亭經營者蓮姐合照，透露蓮姐下月搬去距現址不遠、現時大帽山郊野公園訪客中心旁的茶水亭。早前政府為大帽山茶水亭公開招標，惹人關注蓮姐的命運。"},{"pid":"40ef4a642a42ac4ada273a36101060e9a3bdd8c5","tid":1915192,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"好希望入面有個係武肺隱性病患者"},{"pid":"e750cafb0e2f341de409014a9fb695f110e4e9f6","tid":1915192,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:13:40.000Z","msg":"隨便搵舊石掉佢仲好"},{"pid":"12c09daebe6871b775eef75aa02df643df6fabac","tid":1915192,"uid":47462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"緊係吐佢口水啦，比D祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b773ec1398dd72ea3c730aaec8ccf887d297658","tid":1915192,"uid":156076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"應該落果時唔落<br />\n而家變左過街老鼠先落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}